description: Policy-aware access request intake, compliance check, and approval routing for IT and security teams. A routing agent validates every request against role, manager, and SoD policy before handing off a decision-ready approval packet. Keep Okta and Microsoft Entra as your IdP; replace the Google Form inbox, the Slack permission threads, and the untracked manual approvals around them.
